{"tid":1653380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣人畀咗啲抗爭攻略我哋","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T05:32:00.000Z","uid":307607,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"688e1fd92bfc96ec35b46764008d0bc8ef42a6c0","tid":1653380,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:02:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\">和平示威抗議只有在民主國家有用<br />\n在專制國家沒用<br />\n你和平抗議，結果政府就對你血腥鎮壓</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以香港人要有革命的準備了<br />\n只要七、八百萬香港人團結起來，香港還是有勝算的</span><br />\n香港人應該組織起來，開始準備武器了<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民兵跟正規軍打<br />\n就是要打游擊戰</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不要正面對決<br />\n正面對決，民兵毫無勝算</span><br />\n游擊戰就是打了就跑<br />\n趁你不注意偷襲你<br />\n等你回過神，人早就消失了<br />\n還有就是圍攻落單敵人<br />\n敵人集結時，我方就落跑，敵人落單時，我方就圍起來幹掉<br />\n這就是游擊戰的精髓<br />\n如果有上百萬香港人跟你打游擊戰，四面八方、每個都來偷襲你，打了就落跑<br />\n就算中國解放軍把戰車開到香港也沒屁用<br />\n第一步把香港街道上的所有監視器，全都破壞<br />\n執行任務時，戴安全帽，掩飾身份，保護自身安全<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目標只要每天消滅二、三個敵人即可，甚至只要消滅一個也OK</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">時間一久，積少就會成多</span><br />\n香港暴警是有幾個能消耗？<br />\n中國武警或解放軍又有幾個可以消耗？<br />\n反正香港人是在地人，是地頭蛇，他們就住在香港，哪裡也去不了，有的是時間跟你耗<br />\n而且香港有七、八百萬人，就算犧牲一個，還有千千萬萬個&hellip;<br />\n你解放軍也才二百萬人罷了<br />\n跟你耗個三年、五年、七年、十年&hellip;都無所謂<br />\n美國跑去越南打越戰，打了十幾年，最後失敗離開<br />\n越南是越南人的家，但不是美國人的家<br />\n美國人離鄉背井跑去陌生的越南打十多年的戰爭，打到後面美國大兵心理都快崩潰了<br />\n越南軍隊各方面都不如美軍，但靠著游擊戰，贏得最後的勝利<br />\n<br />\n其實段野幾有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戰略方面唔多講 上面好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n國際戰線嗰邊要同外國講明和平抗爭無用先至慢慢轉成勇武 升級唔係無原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個道理連台灣人都明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1570972375.A.F58.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1570972375.A.F58.html&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAoTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=828ab7a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1570972375.A.F58.html</a>"},{"pid":"a99dddfd6014da215b439895826e2e4a3b0a4754","tid":1653380,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:03:00.000Z","msg":"推1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c82d19a234e8355897e78a404b5c87a581dfa2c","tid":1653380,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"推2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f505ea5afac8601c45725ca8e160b2eee938c374","tid":1653380,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:03:25.000Z","msg":"推3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c632b3ae00e1b9f99cfc881fb260407daa621a","tid":1653380,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫推 p牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c394e1b42e93ae340bea646c603dbc292ebd6a67","tid":1653380,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:04:21.000Z","msg":"推5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8c9d267d79e7a605f1bc282adf4febc16f69ce","tid":1653380,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:04:34.000Z","msg":"推6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eace9159fab72cb8ba41995b96fe0161a9601d22","tid":1653380,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:04:44.000Z","msg":"推7/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5582d3c9085f2c7360297149f65d63ec37d31abd","tid":1653380,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"推8/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abf6